{"tid":2250730,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"[支win]瑞典禁使用華為中興設備電訊商參與5G頻譜拍賣","createTime":"2020-10-20T09:57:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-21T06:44:12.000Z","uid":144626,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd1955613ae16657cfad2a458e4017e58587283","tid":2250730,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:57:27.000Z","msg":"瑞典監管當局周二宣布，禁止使用華為及中興通訊(00763)設備的電訊公司，參與下月舉行5G頻譜拍賣。瑞典郵電局(Swedish Post and Telecom Agency, 簡稱PTS) 發表聲明中稱，已經批准Hi3G Access、Net4Mobility、Telia Sverige及Teracom參與3.5 GHz及2.3 GHz頻譜拍賣。<br />\n<br />\n當局為這些公司核心功能的設備設置了一系列條件。這些核心功能包括無線接入、傳輸和核心網絡、以及維持網絡功能和電子通信服務所必需的服務網絡。<br />\n<br />\nPTS表示，華為和中興的產品不得用於新的核心功能的安裝，核心功能中已經在用的華為和中興產品最遲在2025年1月1日前必須逐步淘汰。<br />\n<br />\nPTS還表示，在2025年1月1日前，必須逐步淘汰依賴外國工作人員或功能的核心功能，並由設在瑞典的功能或工作人員取代。"},{"pid":"707b939548b698d307b28c509edef84c0e02f812","tid":2250730,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"默克爾：德國唔會禁止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0b0fa914e82bde017cfff8834a763a04b11d786","tid":2250730,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"707b939548b698d307b28c509edef84c0e02f812","tid":2250730,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T09:59:09.000Z","msg":"默克爾：德國唔會禁止 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:00:11.000Z","msg":"聞支人: 韓國都唔會禁, 因為5支係出自韓國"},{"pid":"00e2d4b27089afaec7936497de2ee2e8b1259fdc","tid":2250730,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-20T10:00:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"baafd60ce4529e3e0a10d3153c7a2098fac47959","tid":2250730,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci